# Intuit Design System - Size Token Library

## Primitive Size Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--size-1`: 1px
- `--size-2`: 2px
- `--size-16`: 16px
- `--size-20`: 20px
- `--size-24`: 24px
- `--size-28`: 28px
- `--size-40`: 40px
- `--size-48`: 48px
- `--size-60`: 60px
- `--size-64`: 64px
- `--size-80`: 80px
- `--size-100`: 100px
- `--size-120`: 120px

## Semantic Size Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Action
- `--size-action-border`: --size-2 /* The pixel size for actions borders, usually secondary actions. */
- `--size-action-icon-large`: --size-28 /* The pixel size of the icon in large actions. */
- `--size-action-icon-medium`: --size-24 /* The pixel size of the icon in medium actions. */
- `--size-action-icon-small`: --size-16 /* The pixel size of the icon in small actions. */
- `--size-action-min-width-large`: --size-120 /* The minimum width for large actions. */
- `--size-action-min-width-medium`: --size-100 /* The minimum width for medium actions. */
- `--size-action-min-width-small`: --size-80 /* The minimum width for small actions. */
